OL,3,CFormer RUC officer to be prosecuted
OL,4,Cfor murder after ombudsman probe
OL,6,FA former RUC officer is to be
OL,7,Fprosecuted for murder and conspiracy
OL,8,Fto murder following an investigation
OL,9,Fby the Police Ombudsman in Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FOmbudsman Marie Anderson confirmed the
OL,13,Fprosecution following her legacy
OL,14,Finvestigation, called Operation
OL,15,FNewham, which encompasses 125 murders,
OL,16,Flargely attributed to the UVF in the
OL,17,Fmid-Ulster and South Armagh areas of
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and the Republic of
OL,19,FIreland during the 1970s.
