OL,6,FMrs Anderson said: "To publish the
OL,7,Ffull public statement would
OL,8,Fpotentially be prejudicial and I,
OL,9,Ftherefore, gave careful consideration
OL,10,Fto publishing an amended form of the
OL,11,Freport.
OL,13,F"However, given the significant amount
OL,14,Fof linked information, such a report
OL,15,Fwould be so substantially changed that
OL,16,Fit would not present a complete and
OL,17,Fcomprehensive account of the
OL,18,Finvestigation and could be misleading.
