OL,6,F"It is my intention to provide as full
OL,7,Fa narrative as possible of all matters
OL,8,Frelevant to my investigation and its
OL,9,Fconclusions.
OL,11,F"The only viable option open to me,
OL,12,Ftherefore, is to seek an extension to
OL,13,Fthe timeframes permitted under the
OL,14,Ftransitional arrangements of the
OL,15,FLegacy Act for completion of reports
OL,16,Fbefore April 30 2025."
