OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Public
OL,7,FProsecution Service (PPS) said: "We
OL,8,Fcan confirm that a decision was taken
OL,9,Fto prosecute one person reported on a
OL,10,Ffile submitted by the Police Ombudsman
OL,11,Ffor Northern Ireland in connection
OL,12,Fwith their Operation Newham
OL,13,Finvestigation.
OL,15,F"The decision to prosecute the former
OL,16,FRUC officer for offences which include
OL,17,Fmurder and conspiracy to murder was
OL,18,Ftaken in February 2024.
